(39, 1, '2020-10-01 13:52:32', '2020-10-01 13:52:32', '<img src=\"http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/elementor/thumbs/download-1-owafxryp51yqkezn8qwtdhc4j0p01f3h4cjv1x6u0k.png\" title=\"download (1)\" alt=\"download (1)\" />											\n			<h1>TELEMEDHOME</h1>		\n		<p>This HIPAA-complaint IOS application empowers patients, families and medical providers and health care organization collaboratively manage chronical medical conditions at home, with telemedicine functionalities.</p>		\n		<p>WIREFRAMING | PROTOTYPING | UI AND UX DESIGN | IPAD APP DEVELOPMENT</p>		\n			<h1>The Challenge</h1>		\n<p>The Physician-Led Company witnessed a high rate of hospital admissions, morbidity and early mortality rates for the lack a collaborative platform between patients, care givers and family members.</p>\n<p>Â </p>\nÂ 		\n				<figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/Google-Datally-featured-image-768x432.jpg\" alt=\"Google-Datally-featured-image\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/1-2-768x406.jpg\" alt=\"1-2\" /></figure>			\n						Previous\n						Next\n			<h4>TelemedHome UI Exploration</h4>		\n			<h1>The Solution</h1>		\n		<p>With a view to develop patients centric application, Telemedhome is built with a clutter free design and highly inituitive interface to help users to focus on keeping track of their health with timely remainders, and remotely moniter high risk patients with chronic diseases.</p>		\n										<img width=\"1024\" height=\"412\" src=\"http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/app-android-1024x412.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/app-android-1024x412.png 1024w, http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/app-android-300x121.png 300w, http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/app-android-768x309.png 768w, http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/app-android-1536x617.png 1536w, http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/app-android.png 1794w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h1>Key Highlights of the Solution</h1>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n										Timely remainders of appointment, daily medications and tasks\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Easy 2-way communication between patient and providers\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Secure HIPAA Complaint Text/Image/Video exchange\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Track process of patient care plan by all the involved user types\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Instant Video Calling with the users not present on the application\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n			<h1>Words From Our Client</h1>		\n							\"Arkenea had done what they can make to each iteration more seamless than the previous one,\"\n							<img width=\"216\" height=\"233\" src=\"http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/download-1.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />						\n														DR. ADRIAN PIELEANU, \n																						Founder, TelemedHome', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'home', '', '', '2020-10-06 12:56:47', '2020-10-06 12:56:47', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wp_theme_test/?page_id=39', 0, 'page', '', 0),
