nt/uploads/2020/10/app-android-768x309.png 768w, http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/app-android-1536x617.png 1536w, http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/app-android.png 1794w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" />											\n			<h1>Key Highlights of the Solution</h1>		\n					<ul>\n							<li>\n										Timely remainders of appointment, daily medications and tasks\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Easy 2-way communication between patient and providers\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Secure HIPAA Complaint Text/Image/Video exchange\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Track process of patient care plan by all the involved user types\n									</li>\n								<li>\n										Instant Video Calling with the users not present on the application\n									</li>\n						</ul>\n			<h1>Words From Our Client</h1>		\n							\"Arkenea had done what they can make to each iteration more seamless than the previous one,\"\n							<img width=\"216\" height=\"233\" src=\"http://localhost/wp_theme_test/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/download-1.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />						\n														DR. ADRIAN PIELEANU, \n																						Founder, TelemedHome\n			<h1>GET IN TOUCH FOR FREE CONSULATION</h1>		\n			<a href=\"#\" role=\"button\">\n						TALK TO US\n					</a>', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '39-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-10-01 19:19:21', '2020-10-01 19:19:21', '', 39, 'http://localhost/wp_theme_test/index.php/2020/10/01/39-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
